  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à Mousepad</title>

    <para>
      <application>Mousepad</application> is a simple
      <application>GTK+ 2</application> text editor for the
      <application>Xfce</application> desktop environment.
    </para>

    &lfs72_checked;

